Info.Title: 95ers: Echoes
Info.Writer: Thomas Gomez Durham (story), James Durham (story), Kip Rasmussen, Thomas Gomez Durham (screenplay)
Info.Actors: Alesandra Durham, Joel Bishop, Terence Goodman, K. Danor Gerald
Info.Plot: An FBI agent with time-bending powers must fight sinister forces from the future to save her loved ones from being erased from existence.
